&gt; 	    Currently there is no way to do this.  It is a recognized problem
&gt; 	but I believe that there's been difficulty finding someone willing to go
&gt; 	through the process of developing (and defending) a proposal for doing
&gt; 	network name lookup.
&gt; 	
&gt; 	Craig
&gt; 	
&gt; I thought there was an IETF Working Group (domains?) chartered to take
&gt; care of this?  I recall discussion of it at Annapolis, I believe.

Bob:

    I wouldn't be surprised if there was a move to create a working group.
I believe, in fact, that such a working group has been proposed informally
at least three times (at the Ames meeting(!), the Annapolis meeting and
I believe again in Ann Arbor).  The problem has been the lack of someone
willing to commit a month to sorting through the various ideas and producing
a proposal.

Craig

